好垃圾 政府呢幾年成日出維穩廣告<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/000934_631aaef922a2fa6270cef3677158ca1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F000934_631aaef922a2fa6270cef3677158ca1b.jpg&h=d3f794ed&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個係港鐵廣告喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條數咪又係賣地加價壞車換番黎"},{"pid":"4963361f37f68384f944586b8d56ec4e5d16a396","tid":368551,"uid":52132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:12:51.000Z","msg":"我都想問 成日係到播<br />\n超支真係多得啲廣告唔少"},{"pid":"cdf336419a277e7d79d308247763196a5cf719a7","tid":368551,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:35:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好垃圾 政府呢幾年成日出維穩廣告<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/22/000934_631aaef922a2fa6270cef3677158ca1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F22%2F000934_631aaef922a2fa6270cef3677158ca1b.jpg&h=d3f794ed&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個係港鐵廣告喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSor <br />\n所以我就係問到底邊個找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣即係一個就政府賣 <br />\n一個就港鐵賣<br />\n 因為總共有兩個<br />\n另一個一定係政府 因為出左政府logo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n不過講到尾 <br />\n政府係港鐵大股東 已且港鐵啲錢邊到黎大家都心照<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1a160477bf13012b12024eaa99af1836bd3543","tid":368551,"uid":41849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:47:02.000Z","msg":"咪你搭車 供樓D錢囉"},{"pid":"7db2a44ace18c4b990b9925b056597a8cf78a806","tid":368551,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:37:46.000Z","msg":"納稅人"}]}